<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type'/>
    <style>
      body { margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif; }
      .banner { background-color: #5B34EA; padding-top: 2%; padding-bottom: 2%; width: 100%; }
      .mail { align-items: center; text-align: center; color: #777683; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif; }
      .container { max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 20px; color: #1D1A31; }
      .header { padding-top: 40px; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-weight: 800; font-size: 24px; line-height: 33px; color: #5B34EA; }
      .confirm-button { border-radius: 20px; background: #5B34EA; text-align: center; display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; margin: 16px 0; }
      .confirm-button a { font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 12px; line-height: 16px; color: #FFFFFF !important; text-decoration: none; }
      .features { text-align: left; max-width: 400px; margin: 24px auto; }
      .features li { margin: 8px 0; }
      hr { margin: 40px 0 24px; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #ddd; }
      .footer-container { text-align: center; width: 100%; }
      #footer { max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto; display: inline-block; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="mail">
      <div class="container">
        <%= image_tag "Banner.svg", class: "banner", alt: "banner" %>
        <p class="header">Welcome to Miru!</p>

        <p>Hi <%= @resource.first_name.titleize %> <%= @resource.last_name.titleize %>,</p>

        <p>We are so delighted to have you onboard. We want to let you know some of the best ways to get up and running on our portal:</p>

        <ul class="features">
          <li>Send professional invoices Instantly</li>
          <li>Send and accept payments from clients seamlessly</li>
          <li>Manage your team and track their progress</li>
          <li>Track your time and overall expenses easily</li>
        </ul>

        <p>We'd like to make sure we got your email address right!</p>

        <p class="confirm-button"><%= link_to 'Confirm my email address', confirmation_url(@resource, confirmation_token: @token) %></p>

        <hr />

        <p>If you did not create this account, please ignore this email.</p>

        <p>Cheers,<br/>Team Miru</p>
      </div>

      <%= render "devise/shared/footer" %>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
